items.checkin_comment: #MCBCAdventCalendar 2024 - Day 6 - Sweet tropical aromas with stonefruit notes. Creamy mouthfeel. Amarillo, Sabro, Simcoe & Peacherine giving sweet, juicy stonefruit flavours midpalate. Coconut, Peaches, Mango, Passionfruit. Low bitterness. Summer sipper!
